---
import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from 'swiper/astro';
import 'swiper/css';
import 'swiper/css/effect-cards';
---
<section class="py-24 bg-primary/5">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
      Noo ngi ñaan Sunu Boroom yàggal sen dund te dolli len wér barkeb ki moom Tuubaa
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="group" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/serigne-mountakha.jpg" 
            alt="Serigne Mountakha Mbacké"
            class="w-full h-[650px] object-cover object-top"
          >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/90 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-8 transform translate-y-6 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Serigne Mountakha Mbacké</h3>
              <p class="text-white/90 text-lg">Khalife Général des Mourides</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="group" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <img 
            src="/serigne-amdy.jpg" 
            alt="Serigne Amdy Khady Fall"
            class="w-full h-[650px] object-cover object-top"
          >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/90 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-8 transform translate-y-6 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-500">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Serigne Amdy Khady Fall</h3>
              <p class="text-white/90 text-lg">Khalife Général des Baye Fall</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-12">Témoignages</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl text-white">"</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              "Participer au financement des ndogous collectifs est une façon pour moi de me sentir connecté à ma communauté même depuis l'étranger. C'est une tradition qui nous définit et nous rassemble."
              <footer class="mt-4 text-primary font-medium">- Abdoul, disciple mouride</footer>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl text-white">"</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              "Les ndogous collectifs sont bien plus qu'un simple repas. C'est un moment d'unité, de partage et de spiritualité qui nous permet de vivre pleinement notre foi et nos traditions."
              <footer class="mt-4 text-primary font-medium">- Fatou, bénévole</footer>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>